[[File:Arvel chathead.png|left]]
'''Arvel''' is one of the many [[Elf|Elven]] citizens of [[Lletya]]. Arvel is distrustful of adventurers, and will talk to the player about how they often cause as much trouble as they put right. She offers the parting advice "always do the right thing" when the conversation ends.

The player can only access Arvel to [[Thieving#Pickpocketing|pickpocket]] after starting [[Mourning's End Part I]] and require level 85 [[Thieving]]. A successful pickpocket yields [[coins]] or other items and 353.3 [[Thieving]] experience.

